reviews:
The receiver itself seems well constructed, but the no swivel design is horrible. No matter how much torque you put on it, the receiver constantly sways side to side which wedges itself into your tires.
Was expecting a much better product from CURT.
This is a toque is great. I have purchased two , I have one at the house and one at work. You can purchase this knowing you are getting great quality from Carhartt

A great product from Amazon! Have been waiting to purchase this clock and am glad I did. Clock is very easy to setup out of the box put the batteries in, hold the blue button and ask Alexa to pair your clock and it sets the time itself.
Love setting timers with Alexa and it’s even better now that I can see on the clock how much time is left.

I wish I would have purchased this wireless charger months ago. Have an otter box on my phone and sometimes a pain to open up the flap on the bottom to get to the charging port, but not now simply place the phone on the wireless charger and the device starts charging.

review_title: Anker knows how to make great products
reviews: Anker does an amazing job with their products. Packaged perfectly, beautiful design, excellent products with an exceptional warranty. Anytime I need a charger/cable/battery pack I go straight to Anker.

review_title: It’s Paper towel and it works
reviews: What can you say it’s Bounty, it cleans up your mess very well. I do like the select-a- size rolls, normally only need half a sheet of Bounty to clean up anyways.

They are great containers with screw on lids, so no worries of the lid popping open. I used to always use Tupperware containers for lunch, but now I find myself going to these every morning they are very convenient to have.

I really like this holster, but unfortunately the velcro doesn’t not hold up. I’ve been using this for just over a week and already have issues with the velcro keeping the case closed. I have had my phone fall out of the case twice. I wish the case had a snap to help reinforce the velcro.

Great shave cream. Has a nice scent but not overwhelming.
This is a bit pricey, but seems to be worth it with all the natural ingredients.
Have had no issues with skin irritations or rash, and am very pleased with this product.
Customer service could not be better. They contacted me before arrival stating if there are any issues to please contact them.
Rocky Mountain, keep up the great work. I will definitely be purchasing more.

Very nice product. Has a nice scent and not a greasy residue afterwards. Nicely packaged and bottle/pump works perfectly. Great job Rocky Mountain Barber Company, reached out to me before the arrival of the product to contact them if there are any issues. This is great customer service.
Will definitely be ordering more once I run out.

This belt really defeats the purpose of wearing a belt. You can not wear this belt snug, if you do the buckle constantly releases. Would be a great belt if it would not release with a slight movement or tug, better design on the clasp is needed.

Anker makes EXCELLENT products.
Works much better then any other products.
Don’t waste money or time and just buy Anker

Anker is simply the best.
Love all products I have received from them.
These products work flawlessly and work better then originals.
Very pleased with the quality of these curtains, darken room well.
Product works great! Hot or cold it does the trick. Will definitely be purchasing more Yeti products.
Great product and will definitely purchase more. Was skeptical if this product would work as well as they say it does, but it does. Keeps drinks nice and cool hours after opening.

review_title: Perfect size Squeegee for small areas
reviews: Very nice squeegee. I travel constantly on the road for work and purchased this to clean side windows and mirrors from snow and slush kick back and it works perfectly. Very pleased with this product.
Such a great book. Easy recipes to follow, 5 ingredients to use, beautiful pictures.
Wife wanted it because of the design....but it is actually a very good pizza cutter nice and sharp and cuts through without any problems.
Nice funnel at a great price. Every garage should have one or two.
Not a fan of the spray at all. Will definitely be sticking with B12 in pill form.
Great set of lego, bought this set to add on to a bigger set. Kids have a blast building whatever they would like, but also nice that it comes with instructions to build set figures.
Absolutely love these! Cheaper buying them in bulk and having them on hand.
Excellent product, wish I bought one a long time ago. Charges much faster than original chargers.
Great product, great length, very well made. Love the little bands they send to keep the cable nice a neat. Well done. Hands down next power outlet/cable will definitely be an Anker product.
Replaced our old mortar with this and couldn't be happier. Nice weight and works perfectly.
Great knife, nice weight and very sharp. Think this might be my new go to knife.

review_title: Excellent product at a great price
reviews: Works very well and doesn't eat up all your soap like some I have used in the past.
Great quality towels and for the price you can't go wrong.
Have always used Mother's products....up until now. Great polish and so easy on and off. Makes your paint/chrome look like a mirror finish.

review_title: Milwaukee tools are simply the best
reviews: Amazing power and battery last forever.
Love these, a great combination for a chocolate bar

This is a great detail cleaner. Leaves the dash looking like the day you drive off the lot. Great at cleaning and doesn't leave any oil residue behind so makes it perfect for steering wheel, navigation screen. Etc. Will definitely be purchasing this again.
Nice quality in both the case and wrench. Only draw back they look so nice I don't like getting them dirty.
Tekton does make some great products and this is one of them. Purchased one to have in the garage and to try out, liked it enough to purchase another to store in the vehicle.
Nice case, seem to be made of good quality. And with a lifetime warranty you can't go wrong.

review_title: Good idea to have in the vehcile
reviews: Have yet to use them but seem to be of the greatest of quality. Nice to have a storage bag to keep things neat and tidy.

review_title: A new look on salt and pepper
reviews: A little hard to fill but they look great and the wife loves them.
Love the glasses but glass is pretty thin. Have boughten two batches of these no problems with the first but after receiving the second and placing them in the dishwasher one glass came out broken.
Great for running those tools that need the extra power. Use on my circular saw and impact guns.
Light is nice and bright. I purchased two of these had an issue with one of them. Contacted customer service and they rectified the issue right away, very nice to see them stand behind their product.
These are a must if you are running either circular saw or reciprocating saw. Provides your tools with excellent amount of power and charge lasts to get the job done.

review_title: For the handyman this is a go to power tool.
reviews: This is an excellent power tool. Very useful to have around the house for many repairs, also the battery does seem to hold a charge better than most power tools that I have used.

Installed yesterday in no time. Very simple to switch wires over to new bracket, snap on the thermostat, activate WiFi and sit back and enjoy the power of having your heating system at your finger tips at all times.
If you have a grill this is a must...makes cleaning a breeze.
Have ordered two of these now and the second one I ordered seems like it is made with a much more durable material, more of a canvas rather than vinyl. Looks great on the back of the Jeep
Looks much better than the stock antenna, and seems to have slightly better reception.
Fast shipping and is an excellent product. This is my second time purchasing this product ( for a new watch ). Worked flawlessly on the first watch I had.
Easy to install...great fit and look great.
